wdi2-TM.TAX.MRCH.SR.ZS.def: Share of tariff lines with specific rates is the share of lines in the tariff schedule that are set on a per unit basis or that combine ad valorem and per unit rates.
wdi2-TM.TAX.MRCH.SR.ZS.name: Share of tariff lines with specific rates
wdi2-TM.TAX.MRCH.SR.ZS.source: World Bank staff estimates using the World Integrated Trade Solution system, based on data from United Nations Conference on Trade and Development's Trade Analysis and Information System (TRAINS) database.
